<Link id="l00259" /><CodeLine lineNumber="259"><Highlight kind="comment">/// This may be linked to the process&#39;s working directory, or maintain its own.</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00263" /><CodeLine lineNumber="263"><Highlight kind="comment">/// A more principled approach would be to push this down a level, modelling</Highlight></CodeLine>
